<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2013/05/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>CopilotStudioHealthMonitor</id>
    <version>1.0.8</version>
    <title>Copilot Studio Agent Health Monitor</title>
    <authors>Manmohan</authors>
    <owners>Manmohan</owners>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/manmohanbca-spec/CopilotStudioHealthMonitor</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/manmohanbca-spec/CopilotStudioHealthMonitor/master/icon.png</iconUrl>
    <licenseUrl>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/manmohanbca-spec/CopilotStudioHealthMonitor/master/LICENSE</licenseUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>An XrmToolBox plugin to audit, secure, and validate Microsoft Copilot Studio agents across Power Platform / Dataverse environments.

Features:
- Dashboard: KPI cards and risk-ranked agent table with health colour coding
- Agent Inventory: Full agent list with filter, owner info, auth mode, solution membership, and expandable bot components
- Security Scanner: Automated 0-100 security score for every agent (SEC-01 No Auth, SEC-03 HTTP Actions, SEC-05 Orphaned Owner, SEC-07 Not in Solution) with per-issue remediation steps
- Deployment Readiness: Four pre-deployment checks (DEP-01 through DEP-04) with optional target-org verification
- ALM Diff: Side-by-side bot component comparison across two environments (Match / Content Differs / Missing in Target / Only in Target)

Read-only - never writes to your environment. Requires Dataverse online with Copilot Studio enabled.</description>
    <summary>Audit, secure and validate Copilot Studio agents across Power Platform environments from within XrmToolBox.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
1.0.8 - Use real XrmToolBox dependency version 1.2023.10.67 (1.2024.9.69 didn't exist on nuget.org which caused xrmtoolbox.com validator to reject as "version dependency missing")
1.0.7 - Wrap XrmToolBox dependency in &lt;group targetFramework="any"&gt; with range version
1.0.6 - Switched to iconUrl and removed NuGet 5+ features (icon/license/readme elements) to fix xrmtoolbox.com validator dependency format
1.0.5 - Updated nuspec to 2013 schema; DLL target net472
1.0.4 - Fixed DLL target path to lib\net452\Plugins
1.0.3 - Fixed NuGet dependency ID to XrmToolBox
1.0.2 - Flattened NuGet dependency format
1.0.1 - Added 128x128 icon; fixed license expression and readme in package
1.0.0 - Initial release: Dashboard, Agent Inventory, Security Scanner, Deployment Readiness, ALM Diff
    </releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright (c) 2026 Manmohan</copyright>
    <language>en-US</language>
    <tags>XrmToolBox Dataverse PowerPlatform CopilotStudio MicrosoftCopilot Security ALM Deployment Bot Plugin Dynamics365</tags>
    <dependencies>
      <group targetFramework="any">
        <dependency id="XrmToolBox" version="[1.2023.10.67, )" />
      </group>
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="bin\Release\CopilotStudioHealthMonitor.dll" target="lib\net452\Plugins" />
  </files>
</package>
